    "cross_region": "Parent-region terms (кольский / kola peninsula / arctic circle) appear in the variants of MULTIPLE canonicals — that's how a single 'Кольский полуостров' query expands to every Murmansk canonical (Хибины + Колвица + Ловозеро + …) and matches all their photos."
